briefdescription.para: Wrapper class for the FFTW complex types 'fftw_complex'.

detaileddescription.para: This class encapsulates the low-level complex number types provided by the FFTW Fast Fourier Transform library (i.e. 'fftw_complex', 'fftwf_complex', 'fftwl_complex'). In particular, it provides constructors, member functions and arithmetic operators that make FFTW complex numbers compatible with std::complex. In addition, the class defines transformations to polar coordinates and accessors.
FFTWComplex implements the concepts AlgebraicField and DivisionAlgebra. The standard image types FFTWRealImage and FFTWComplexImage are defined.
